---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
export const prerender = true;
<Base title="Cancellation Policy | Golf Graeagle" description="Cancellation Policy for GolfGraeagle.com bookings — Zoomaway Technologies Inc. 72-hour standard cancellation window.">
  <Nav />
  <div style="min-height:100vh;padding:clamp(100px,12vw,140px) clamp(20px,5vw,48px) 80px;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p style="font-size:11px;color:#e8a850;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px;">Legal</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 12px;line-height:1.1;">Cancellation Policy</h1>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(240,248,242,0.3);margin:0 0 56px;">GolfGraeagle.com · Operated by Zoomaway Technologies Inc.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Highlight box — the key policy fact -->
    <div class="reveal" style="background:rgba(82,168,98,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(82,168,98,0.18);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;">
        <span style="font-size:24px;flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>
        <div>
          <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:500;color:rgba(120,196,136,0.95);margin:0 0 10px;">72-Hour Standard Cancellation Window</h2>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(240,248,242,0.6);line-height:1.7;margin:0;">Zoomaway provides its clientele with a 72-hour cancellation policy for all its services, except for large group outings which are defined by an individual contract provided to the group leader.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(240,248,242,0.65);line-height:1.8;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;">

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">Zoomaway Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>Zoomaway provides its clientele with a 72-hour cancellation policy for all its services except for large group outings which are defined by an individual contract provided to the group leader.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;">Cancellation policies for certain clients can vary and Zoomaway will pass on the vendor's (host) cancellation policy to its customers.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;">Zoomaway (and its subsidiaries and web products) provide travel bookings and other tourism-related products. Individual and Group cancellation policies are supported and outlined in all our technology pieces and customers must agree to these policies before proceeding to finishing their transactions.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">Group Outings</h2>
        <p>Large group outings operate under a separate individual contract provided to the group leader. The specific cancellation terms for your group booking will be defined in that contract. Please review your group contract carefully before confirming your booking.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">Vendor Policies</h2>
        <p>For bookings involving third-party vendors (golf courses, lodging properties, restaurants), Zoomaway will pass on the vendor's cancellation policy to its customers. Applicable vendor policies will be communicated to you at the time of booking.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(240,248,242,0.06);padding-top:32px;">
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(240,248,242,0.3);">Questions about your booking or cancellation? Contact us at <a href="mailto:mike.eskuchen@golfthehighsierra.com" style="color:#e8a850;">mike.eskuchen@golfthehighsierra.com</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Base>
